This is auscompgeek's JavaScript IRC bot.
This bot is designed to be run with JSDB, found at <http://jsdb.org/>.

Features:
	- General flood protection.
	- Logging.
	- Remote control.

Calculator features:
	- Error reporting.
	- Dice.
	- Temperature conversion.

Basic usage (this will connect the bot to 127.0.0.1):
	aucgbot.start();

Advanced usage:
	aucgbot.nick = "nick";
	aucgbot.prefs[pref] = setting;
	aucgbot.start(server, port, ident, pass, channels);

